</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="1" ind2=" " tag="561">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Illuminated for a member of the Albertini family of Nola (their arms, f. 1r); 17th-century inscription, Stefano Scarella di San Remo (f. 102v).</marc:subfield>
</marc:datafield>
    <marc:datafield ind1="1" ind2=" " tag="561">
  <marc:subfield code="a">Sold at auction at Sotheby's, 23 June 1992, lot 73, to Lawrence J. Schoenberg.</marc:subfield>
